text: Josef Buchner (born 16 May 1974) is a German skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1998 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:German male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Germany Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:People from Traunstein
